++++++++++++==##==++++++++++++

       Vir2 Electri6ity       

++++++++++++==##==++++++++++++

Electri6ity contains 
eight of the most famous and 
distinguished guitar tones 
from the history of the 
instrument. More than 24,000 
24-bit samples were taken of 
each guitar. Three pickup 
options (front, rear, and 
mixed) are available on every 
guitar. An impressive amount 
of samples allow you to play 
every articulation on every 
fret of every string for an 
absolutely authentic guitar 
sound. Downstrokes, upstrokes, 
seamless velocity layers, 
ghost notes, mutes, 
harmonics, hammer-ons, 
pulloffs, slides, releases, 
and FX...the sky is the limit 
with Electri6ity.
